main event: Two bright red objects were observed over Miami, Fla. and away at high speed.
interesting points: The objects were very bright and hovered for several minutes.
A second object appeared and suddenly darted up and out of sight at a terrific rate of speed.
The witness, Mrs. [redacted], lives near the airport and is accustomed to observing aircraft, and she is convinced that the objects reported were neither meteors nor aircraft.
The witness saw several 'comet-like' objects and other astronomical phenomena.
The document states that the witness, Mrs. [redacted], saw two bright objects on the evening of July 15 around 10:15 pm.
